value = if a then b else c
thing if a
thing if a then b


>> 'true' if True else 'false'
'true'
>>> 'true' if False else 'false'
'false'



With a filter, you need:

[ EXP for x in seq if COND ]

Without a filter you need:

[ EXP for x in seq ]

a = [51,27,13,56]
dict(enumerate(a))

will produce

{0: 51, 1: 27, 2: 13, 3: 56}

